<div class="story"><p>Four Seasons is one of the newest and largest ocean to sound communities in Duck with just over 120 building lots, all large enough to hold a large house and pool. This is a gated community and among the amenities it offers are  a clubhouse, health club, indoor pool, outdoor pool, playground, park, tennis courts and an ocean access and a sound access. You can find Four Seasons just past the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/amy-acres.asp" title="Amy Acres">Amy Acres</a> and before you get to <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/seapines.asp" title="Seapines">Seapines</a>. </p>
